{"tid":2321571,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實返醫護  每日既生態係點","createTime":"2020-12-11T14:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T07:50:21.000Z","uid":133977,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"806785063e66452b677829777601ac1e0d536834","tid":2321571,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"我自己唔係醫護  我由頭到尾都冇wfh<br />\n呢個都算  我當同平時一樣既返工時間<br />\n但工作關係要周圍走 好多時去完過幾日棟樓就有確診  (已經試左幾獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家每日個心態好似上戰場咁唔知自己幾時死<br />\n日日咁搞法隨時有一次中招  <br />\n人地係聚會 買球拍  跳老舞中招  我就被迫  (唔好同我講你可以辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日都覺得自己中左招  又流鼻水又乾咳<br />\n但檢測完都係陰性<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己好慘   但我起碼叫間接會奶野  醫護係直頭面對面咁搞<br />\n我依家都覺得日日都好似會死咁   到底醫護班人係真係為愛定為責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到其他同事wfh   hea呀打機訓教都算   安全最重要<br />\n我就跑生跑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5fd7addb86abb45d755800ac3fd46cb8f46e68","tid":2321571,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"標題打錯   每日心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeca3fd6156c430c40bbd32a03cd2323b0be3b48","tid":2321571,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0277c27e97c362930e9cfd70ccbc63cb1107580","tid":2321571,"uid":321262,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"覺得佢地會驚因為自己萬一瀨嘢而害到其他人，而變到疑神疑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200718a8b6aab086bb2b51f7adfdc5eafb13c0e4","tid":2321571,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f0277c27e97c362930e9cfd70ccbc63cb1107580","tid":2321571,"uid":321262,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"覺得佢地會驚因為自己萬一瀨嘢而害到其他人，而變到疑神疑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"我已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我唔同醫護<br />\n醫護係入之前已經知會面對呢D逆正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e878ea6b7102933a491c89391aa4c46e27f729b","tid":2321571,"uid":193614,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"老實講句wor 你入得醫院做預左wor"},{"pid":"158bbf07b4eec0db3142f908c1ee1d61e1b27b5a","tid":2321571,"uid":227271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T19:42:40.000Z","msg":"呢D野總要有人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似街都要有人洗有人掃<br />\n<br />\n公廁都要有人清潔（鴨脷洲公廁例外）<br />\n<br />\n佢地都係預左惡頂<br />\n<br />\n但問佢地想唔想頂，正常人都唔想啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但職責所在邊有得唔頂（收左人工）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個仆街港共奶支共奶到不顧市民生死<br />\n<br />\n諗下由第一波都依家，係邊個搞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢中 ，興回支 ，跳老舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然唔小得港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關又唔封，一車車免檢落黎永續支那肺炎"},{"pid":"fcd6ea94de4fe8d7a04b7e0c3db113cbe12071be","tid":2321571,"uid":190811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T19:50:15.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩flat mate鬼中晒咪又馬照跑舞照跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8d8788304fbb21a6582aabfb4be4cf7ca181c4","tid":2321571,"uid":283442,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:35:15.000Z","msg":"識幾個醫護朋友<br />\n佢地真係當just a flu 唔驚"},{"pid":"4336b358a6e376a503d1f7c776245b037e0bfba0","tid":2321571,"uid":71915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"806785063e66452b677829777601ac1e0d536834","tid":2321571,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"我自己唔係醫護  我由頭到尾都冇wfh<br />\n呢個都算  我當同平時一樣既返工時間<br />\n但工作關係要周圍走 好多時去完過幾日棟樓就有確診  (已經試左幾獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家每日個心態好似上戰場咁唔知自己幾時死<br />\n日日咁搞法隨時有一次中招  <br />\n人地係聚會 買球拍  跳老舞中招  我就被迫  (唔好同我講你可以辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日都覺得自己中左招  又流鼻水又乾咳<br />\n但檢測完都係陰性<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己好慘   但我起碼叫間接會奶野  醫護係直頭面對面咁搞<br />\n我依家都覺得日日都好似會死咁   到底醫護班人係真係為愛定為責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到其他同事wfh   hea呀打機訓教都算   安全最重要<br />\n我就跑生跑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:36:05.000Z","msg":"前牌我嗰間醫院有幾個確診病人<br />\n<br />\n再加上我曾經同有確診病人部門嘅同事食飯<br />\n<br />\n好彩冇中<br />\n<br />\n其實都好擔心自己會中招野比屋企人<br />\n<br />\n所以今年年中已經搬咗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n到自己真係肯定冇事先會返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"2583ebcea0688a06ee75739a41a42f480cd0ec3f","tid":2321571,"uid":67049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd86aff1df583147812daf27295075678f976cc0","tid":2321571,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:39:15.000Z","msg":"無驚過<br />\n多左個機會搵錢<br />\n去高危地區工作 <br />\n又有每日500津貼<br />\n又有每日500酒店津貼<br />\n<br />\n生活其實無點大變 不過可能對個人衛生注重左<br />\n<br />\n利申 外科 做左幾日全民檢測<br />\n去左高危地區客串兩個月"},{"pid":"06f004d9ad26864b864b53505876e2974046a780","tid":2321571,"uid":233643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7a8d8788304fbb21a6582aabfb4be4cf7ca181c4","tid":2321571,"uid":283442,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:35:15.000Z","msg":"識幾個醫護朋友<br />\n佢地真係當just a flu 唔驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:39:20.000Z","msg":"反而呢條傻西樓主日日驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫佢睇下死亡率同康復率先啦 cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94010bf98df162eef50d10ef2cc688155dafb7e6","tid":2321571,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8736666456ac25b13735def7da9e507df903788e","tid":2321571,"uid":39703,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"做得呢份工 就預左要面對唔同傳染病<br />\n只係垃圾政府搞到咁 明明香港人咁早預防戴哂口罩<br />\n<br />\n返dirty team已經返工麻木 因為都已經爆到第四波<br />\n開頭第一二波 真係會驚 始終沙士個時仲係小學雞<br />\n同男朋友講埋遺言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過full gear 捱下捱下又一日 又一星期 又一個月 而家又就快一年 <br />\n呢一年我自己都冇點出街/聚餐<br />\n入team就自己一個獨來獨往 每日就係返工同放工 放假都係留係屋企 好彩仲有貓陪我<br />\n準備過lonely christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b39fd5ba2b418acb90bb1b06a9ca9d6089f971","tid":2321571,"uid":75777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0277c