得自己中左招  又流鼻水又乾咳<br />\n但檢測完都係陰性<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己好慘   但我起碼叫間接會奶野  醫護係直頭面對面咁搞<br />\n我依家都覺得日日都好似會死咁   到底醫護班人係真係為愛定為責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到其他同事wfh   hea呀打機訓教都算   安全最重要<br />\n我就跑生跑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"我的生態就是：日間工作，和大部分人工作時間幾乎一樣。<br />\n冇驚過感染，感染控制做得好好，自己醫院都冇醫護人員因為醫護工作中招。<br />\n利申：護士"},{"pid":"77f4d8ec8327f655b62a3d03b7693f2419efed35","tid":2321571,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"你畢業咩人工呀，你個職系咩定位你第一日知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔駛燒腦，9成9都有哂程序畀你做<br />\n你畀返一半人工畀我，你幫我wfh囉"},{"pid":"d6407b088e0184c91a71c128b06fa6bb4012b2c3","tid":2321571,"uid":2206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"實有人話收咁高人工預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實情係今年醫護凍薪 罷工救港又扣人工 <br />\n<br />\n黑狗就爽加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9303704189e3b58cb56718c6a2353c02127dae5d","tid":2321571,"uid":313839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}